proletariat.... The conflict... at the fin de siecle was conceived as
a struggle to preserve society's norms and thus to protect the normal
against the abnormal.... The term degeneration had been coined in 1857
in order to characterize those whose nerves had been shattered by poison
like alcohol and opium, through inherited bodily malfunctions, but also by
